data.description: Nestled in the La Cuesta track of La Palma you will find the neighborhood takes pride in their ownership. This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a perfect blend of comfort and style. Upon entering you will step into a spacious living room with vaulted ceilings allowing the natural light that fills the room. Just in time for winter, grab a blanket and enjoy the crackling sounds of the fireplace. The remodeled kitchen boasts exquisite soapstone countertops, sleek glass cabinets, decorative backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances. A large breakfast bar for dining or perfect for hosting a buffet. Dining area features a lovely built-in china hutch. The master bedroom is complete with a modern remodeled bathroom complete with clear-glass barn-style shower door, bidet, and contemporary fixtures. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for family, guests, or even a home office. One bedroom has a convenient Murphy bed, perfect for optimizing space and transforming the room as needed. Let the magic unfold in the backyard. Beautifully landscaped with pavers that create a picturesque patio area. Entertain your family and friends around the cozy gas firepit, creating the ideal ambiance for those warm summer evenings and cool autumn nights. Artificial grass allows you to enjoy that glass of lemonade under the retractable patio shade…a haven for outdoor lovers! This home is not only aesthetically pleasing but also environmentally conscious. Featuring solar panels, providing energy efficiency and potential cost savings. CA appreciates water conserving homes. Decorative rain barrels collect the air-conditioning condensation and rain and distributes into your landscaping. Conveniently located to top-rated schools according to Great Schools website, (including Oxford Academy with testing requirements) parks, shopping, entertainment, and transportation. In summary, this house is a perfect combination of classic charm and satisfaction.
